"Kuri Ifashayobora ya:  Icyo ari cyo cyose Ibintu ya:  . ni Bihari i Iboneza "
"Ikiganiro , na in Ikindi Ibiganiro Nka . "

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:612
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To employ What's This help, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
